---
title: Creamy Mustard Pork Steak with Potato Mash & Capsicum Salad
description: Say hello to comfort with a kick! Juicy pork steaks get the creamy mustard treatment, served up with buttery mash and a zesty veggie salad for a dinner that’s equal parts hearty and fresh.

*We’ve replaced the broccoli in this recipe with capsicum due to local
ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe
card!*

